        <updateDate>2021-02-26T20:31:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[   <p class="MsoNormal"><b style="">Servicemembers Self-Defense Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill allows members of the Armed Forces to carry firearms on military installations and other Department of Defense properties and to generally carry concealed firearms, subject to certain state and local restrictions.<br /><strong /></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
